,{"pid":"01f06b014acef18123ce7a6967f81adb7d7a3ebb","tid":2363874,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b02bb7ab45ea0447510e3f5571dc36b70cbe3b","tid":2363874,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"b76d41fce9f6e5cef2ade4a0deb2c9633c4e15a9","tid":2363874,"uid":132698,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"201685d20bdf4ba2f73bc90ef3af2bc8921a14d5","tid":2363874,"uid":82708,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"其實唔關咩牌子車事<br />\n普遍人有牌冇牌好都係冇防禦意識<br />\n唔理有人或車 出事先算<br />\n<br />\n我自己揸車 成日提自己人停車場落咗車 <br />\n唔好企咁近車通道 真係唔知啲車偷位幾時會撞埋嚟<br />\n泊車後波一定著危險警告燈+3-4km/h 車 慢慢入格 <br />\n提防有人喺車後通過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n段片揸車果個固然唔啱<br />\n但個路人毫無危機感咁行法<br />\n搏司機一定睇到自己呢種心態都有d問題<br />\n我成日都同人講<br />\n千祈唔好行咁近開緊既車既車尾<br />\n就算停左喺度<br />\nd on 9突然後波真係無仇報<br />\n賠幾多俾你但搞到你一身傷又有乜謂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"車尾又驚on9後波，車頭又驚on9 D波。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使行了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"連登質素越黎越下降，叫佢小心啲就等於唔撚行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24a75fc8ee56b566da5dc50201ec00981adbb0e","tid":2363874,"uid":69503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"14bd764eb54a9326da56e48c9c421827ffd25902","tid":2363874,"uid":111872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"點解tesla 咁多on9 野<br />\n究竟係車問題定係吸引到on9 買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n段片條友泊車唔睇左右又唔睇後<br />\n倒車仲要比油（電）<br />\n撞完落車仲要好似怪人係佢後面行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事冇樣野係正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"因為survial bias<br />\n「Tesla 每xx m milea 撞一次」<br />\n<br />\n嘩tesla 好危險呀，好唔成熟呀！<br />\n<br />\n完全唔明點解可以唔需要通過比較數據黎得出「好危險」既結論。<br />\n<br />\n自己之後再查證發現非tesla 車撞車每miles 係10倍，I.e. 非tesla 係危險十倍<br />\n<br />\n咁點解會有呢個反差，因為非tesla 車係唔會上到新聞，只會上到數據庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"ce9a537c520291928096ed559ea715b81f5fce28","tid":2363874,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50a152e607953c207b199391e1bf1d221c9fb647","tid":2363874,"uid":130721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"想請教下，如果我係俾tsela撞到果個人，想和解，收幾多錢睇醫生好？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"都要睇幾傷先話得埋"},{"pid":"853e46fb074a7e630ed72662a5fe733b78ce3b15","tid":2363874,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"後面架車跟得咁貼，佢點泊？"}]}